  <official_title>Long-term Follow-up Study of Participants Following an Open Label, Multi-centre, Phase I/II Dose Escalation Trial of a Recombinant Adeno-associated Virus Vector for Gene Therapy of Adults and Children With Achromatopsia Owing to Defects in CNGB3</official_title>
