  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a longer-term follow-up study for patients who participated in a clinical trial
      of AAV - CNGB3 retinal gene therapy for patients with achromatopsia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The follow up study is designed to collect data on longer-term safety and efficacy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
